title: TDZ Or Not TDZ, There Is No Question 5/11: Ed Norton, AMC, Housing, Donald Glover, Students For Trump

description:
On this edition of TDZ Or Not TDZ, There Is No Question Jack and Miles discuss Ed Norton joining 'Knives Out 2" cast, AMC vs. Wall Street, NY Mayoral Candidates failing "Price of Housing" Question, Twitter teaching Donald Glover that context is dead, and 'Students For Trump' founder being sentenced for posing as lawyer.
